OL,3,CDrivers urged not to text behind the
OL,4,Cwheel in new Sussex campaign
OL,6,FCouncils across Sussex have come
OL,7,Ftogether to launch a 'hard-hitting'
OL,8,Fcampaign to tackle a growing problem
OL,9,Fof drivers using their phone behind
OL,10,Fthe wheel.
OL,12,FLaunched by East Sussex County
OL,13,FCouncil, West Sussex County Council
OL,14,Fand Brighton and Hove City Council, it
OL,15,Fhighlights the consequences of using a
OL,16,Fphone whilst driving.
OL,18,FThe campaign tells drivers that 'one
OL,19,Fsecond of distraction' is a 'lifetime
OL,20,Fof regret'.
