OL,3,CDrivers urged not to text behind the
OL,4,Cwheel in new Sussex campaign
OL,6,FIn Sussex one in five 17-24 year olds
OL,7,Fhave confessed to video calling whilst
OL,8,Fdriving, and the campaign hopes to
OL,9,Ftackle this poor behaviour.
OL,11,FWatch: A video released by Councils
OL,12,Fhighlighting the dangers of texting
OL,13,Fwhilst driving.
OL,15,FThe message will be shared across the
OL,16,Fcounty, with campaign posters on buses
OL,17,Fand at petrol stations.
