OL,3,CDrivers urged not to text behind the
OL,4,Cwheel in new Sussex campaign
OL,6,FIt will also be broadcast on local
OL,7,Fradio, and shared on social media,
OL,8,Fincluding on Snapchat, YouTube,
OL,9,FFacebook and Instagram.
OL,11,FDrivers are four times more likely to
OL,12,Fcrash if using a phone whilst driving,
OL,13,Fand the councils hope people will
OL,14,Flisten.
OL,16,FCllr Claire Dowling, East Sussex
OL,17,FCounty Council's lead member for
OL,18,Ftransport and environment said: "The
OL,19,Fincrease in drivers who admit to
OL,20,Fregularly using their phone behind the
OL,21,Fwheel is extremely worrying.
