OL,3,CDrivers urged not to text behind the
OL,4,Cwheel in new Sussex campaign
OL,6,F"Some drivers underestimate the
OL,7,Fdangers of using a phone whilst
OL,8,Fdriving, even a split-second lapse in
OL,9,Fconcentration whilst changing a song
OL,10,Fon a playlist or checking a text
OL,11,Fmessage can have serious consequences.
OL,13,F"We hope the campaign will highlight
OL,14,Fthose dangers and make people think
OL,15,Ftwice about picking up their phone."
