OL,6,FCllr Joy Dennis, West Sussex County
OL,7,FCouncil's Cabinet Member for Highways
OL,8,Fand Transport, said: "We work hard to
OL,9,Fmake Sussex's roads as safe as
OL,10,Fpossible for all who use them, but we
OL,11,Frely on drivers to do their part. It
OL,12,Fonly takes a short break in
OL,13,Fconcentration on the road ahead for a
OL,14,Fcollision to occur, sometimes with
OL,15,Flife changing impacts.
