OL,3,CDrivers urged not to text behind the
OL,4,Cwheel in new Sussex campaign
OL,6,F"As tempting as it may be to quickly
OL,7,Fread a text or clear a notification,
OL,8,Fit's not worth the risk so we strongly
OL,9,Fhope that this campaign will encourage
OL,10,Fdrivers to ignore their phones and
OL,11,Fgive their full attention to their
OL,12,Fsurroundings, keeping them and all
OL,13,Fother road users safe."
OL,15,FCllr Trevor Muten, Brighton & Hove
OL,16,FCity Council's Cabinet member for
OL,17,FTransport, Parking and Public Realm
OL,18,Fadded: "We've all seen the devastating
OL,19,Fand life-long consequences using a
OL,20,Fphone at the wheel can have.
